text: Milan Stanković (Serbian: Милан Станковић), born September 9, 1987 Yugoslavia (today's Serbia), in the Belgrade city. He sang the song "Ovo je Balkan" in Eurovision Song Contest 2010. He got to the final where he placed 13th out of 25 entries scoring 72 points. == References == Category:1987 births Category:Living people Category:Serbian singers
